description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are on the search for great communicators, those ready to take on a challenge in a fast paced, but rewarding environment, and those that understand the difference between good care and the truly exceptional…&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Portsmouth Hospitals University NHS Trust are seeking &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Qualified and NMC Registered Nurses to join our growing nursing team –we are proud to be developing a team of like-minded individuals, those that can live and breathe our core values, and help us to provide unprecedented levels of care that we know each and every patient deserves. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;We know the secret to our success is through investment in our staff, so in return for your passion, dedication and hard work we promise you: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your choice of placement, based on your skills and experience &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bespoke induction and training programme, based on your needs and aspirations &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tailor made rotational programme for those looking to gain experience all over the hospital&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Relocation package (dependant on criteria)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;On site gym, swimming pool and nursery&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NHS benefits, including pension&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Are you a future leader in the NHS? Let us get you on the right leadership and management pathway to achieve this, with promotional opportunities throughout our clinical service centres. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Our Vision has always been “best care, best people, best performance” - If you are ready to feel valued, and where your work has real meaning, get in contact – we hope to hear from you!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date 30th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
